title: Recap: Tech blanked by OSU in Big 12 opener - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Recap: Tech blanked by OSU in Big 12 opener - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: STILLWATER, Okla. – The Red Raiders fell to seventh-ranked Oklahoma State 7-0 on a no-hitter from Kelly Maxwell in game one of the conference opener Friday night at Cowgirl Stadium.
